  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I assume this is because it writes after the router is disposed, you can override this by using:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nrouter: {...historyRouter(), dispose() {\r\n\r\n      if (typeof window === 'object' && this._onPopState) {\r\n        window.removeEventListener('popstate', this._onPopState);\r\n      }\r\n\r\n\r\n    if (this.writeTimer) {\r\n      clearTimeout(this.writeTimer);\r\n    }\r\n} },\r\n```",
    "created_at": "2021-10-26T12:50:22Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/5389#issuecomment-1367968839",
    "id": 1367968839,
    "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/algolia/instantsearch/issues/5389",
    "node_id": "IC_kwDOAlnbOs5RiYxH",
    "performed_via_github_app": null,
    "pin": null,
    "reactions": {
